# Smart Vending Machine State Machine

## Objective
Simulate a simple vending machine using buttons and LEDs.

## Components
- Arduino UNO
- 3 Push Buttons
- LED
- 220Ω Resistor

## Features
- Coin insertion
- Product selection
- Balance checking
- Product dispensing indication

## Concepts Used
- State Machines
- Digital Inputs
- Serial Communication
- Embedded System Logic
